{"tid":1313443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今時今日 再睇多次天琦呢返說話 好大感受","createTime":"2019-07-13T18:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T18:34:08.000Z","uid":132739,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"28c82c8382012cf8996171bf33599f1cc1caa2e1","tid":1313443,"uid":132739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T18:34:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVEUhAVki0DA&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=628db4e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VEUhAVki0DA</a><br />\n天琦其中以下說話︰<br />\n「我哋呢個社會要攞返我哋應該要有嘅權力<br />\n我哋唔可以再教條主義<br />\n「條條大路通羅馬」<br />\n邊一個方式可以推返呢個政府，呢一個方式就應該要去做<br />\n相信和平抗爭、相信公民抗命嘅人；繼續公民抗命<br />\n相信佔馬路、相信絕食、相信罷交稅等等和平手段嘅人；繼續去做<br />\n我鼓勵你哋去做、我希望你哋去做<br />\n我唔希望你哋因為有人批評你哋嘅手段<br />\n結果完全放棄你哋相信嘅嘢<br />\n同時間，相信勇武抗爭嘅人，一樣都要繼續做」<br />\n<br />\n天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}